Class PartStructureNameComparator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ptc.windchill.enterprise.part.structure.PartStructureNameComparator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Comparator

    public class PartStructureNameComparator
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Comparator
    This Comparator can be used to compare the Name attribute of WTParts and/or WTPartMasters, using a Locale-specific instance of a Collator.

    Supported API: true

    Extendable: false
